    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Subjectively, I feel that small U-turns\n\n```\nx\no  x\nx\n```\n\nstill look a bit more \"glidingly\" than in the originals.\nTo me it looks like the curve is a bit smaller and the visual facing still changes a little faster here than in WW's games.\n\nBut I guess replicating Westwood's movement with 100% accuracy would require far more trial-and-error and presumably more hacky code, and this is enough of an improvement in my eyes.\n:+0.5: because the math is out of my league, so I only tested the PR.\n"
